    "1203104": {
        "Desc": "Stop the affected monsters from getting up the mountain",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Ah, my little friends, there you are."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Miko... what is this? You started eating without us!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "I did, yes. You're paying, after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "The thought of being able to eat the most expensive dishes and drink the finest sake, all for absolutely free... Oh, I just couldn't wait any longer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Ah, Boss, see these two faces here? Remember them. They're the ones picking up the bill later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Okazaki Rikuto",
                    "T": "Alrighty!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uhhh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "What's gotten into you? Come on, sit yourselves down."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "You have to try this fish. It's found exclusively in the waters around Seirai Island. They shipped it to Inazuma overnight, and it was still alive right up until I ordered it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Or maybe you'd rather try this? I know, I know — I normally can't bring myself to drink sake this expensive either."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "If you don't drink alcohol, that's fine too. There are all kinds of fruit juices covering the whole price spectrum."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Grrr... Miko! You are outrageous!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Last time we were here working on the novel, all you ordered for us was the plainest Kushikatsu!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Huh? Strange, I remember no such thing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well I certainly remember it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Kushikatsu and Fried Tofu. That was it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Oh. So what? You did offer to treat me to a meal, didn't you? Anyway, I am something of a VIP, you know. Wouldn't you find it embarrassing to treat me anything short of lavishly?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Miko, this meal is going to be super expensive. Aren't you afraid we won't be able to afford it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Hehe, oh, don't you worry about that. You can most definitely afford it... They're still printing your light novel by the batch, you know. You have quite the generous payment due."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wh—What!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Aaaah, darn it!!! She tricked us into this, {NICKNAME}! Miko was after our Mora from the very beginning!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Shouldn't have let our guard down..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We've been taken for a ride..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Hahaha, oh, the looks on your faces right now. Too perfect. Hahaha."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Oh, by the way — since nobody's wishes came true on the moonless night, novels with incantations are no longer in vogue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "So you'll have to come up with something new for the next chapter of \"The Miraculous Adventures of the Traveler.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "The deadline is looming... I'm counting on you."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1203110": {
        "Desc": "Return to the Grand Narukami Shrine",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Thank you for the meal. I thoroughly enjoyed myself today."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Oh, did I mention? Ei saw that convocation ritual we performed over the Grand Narukami Shrine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "I know she can be pig-headed, but it still took me by surprise when she wrote me a long and sternly worded letter about it, chastising me for \"taking this whole thing much too far.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yae Miko",
                    "T": "Ugh, I hardly see what all the fuss is about. Everyone seemed perfectly happy to me."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
